1. *Staviću* knjigu na policu. (I will put the book on the shelf.)
2. Hoću da *staviš* teg na svoju stranu. (I want you to put the weight on your side.)
3. *Stavićemo* tvoj poklon ispod jelke. (We will put your gift under the Christmas tree.)
4. Da li ćeš mi *staviti* soli u supu? (Will you put salt in my soup?)
5. Kada *staviš* jaja da se kuvaju, računaj 10 minuta. (When you put the eggs to boil, count 10 minutes.)
6. Ako *stavite* ulje u tiganj, onda ćete moći da ispržite ribu. (If you put oil in the pan, then you will be able to fry the fish.)
7. *Stavićete* ručnik u kupatilo pre nego što dođe gost. (You will put a towel in the bathroom before the guest arrives.)
8. Uveče ću *staviti* svoje cipele u ormar. (In the evening, I will put my shoes in the closet.)
9. *Stavićemo* novi tepih na pod u sobi. (We will put a new carpet on the floor in the room.)
10. Da li ćeš mi *staviti* mleko u kafu? (Will you put milk in my coffee?)